<number box="[635,665,1108,1132]" pageId="1" pageNumber="32" value="16.0">16</number>
), abdomen dorsum dull orange and venter dull yellow. Body length 
<number box="[151,263,1143,1167]" pageId="1" pageNumber="32" value="3.5949999999999998" valueMax="3.63" valueMin="3.56">3.56–3.63</number>
(including fore wing); length of head 
<number box="[718,832,1143,1167]" pageId="1" pageNumber="32" value="0.335" valueMax="0.34" valueMin="0.33">0.33–0.34</number>
, width of head: 
<number box="[1028,1143,1143,1167]" pageId="1" pageNumber="32" value="0.75" valueMax="0.76" valueMin="0.74">0.74–0.76</number>
, about 
<number box="[1231,1266,1143,1167]" pageId="1" pageNumber="32" value="2.2">2.2</number>
times of head length; antennae about 
<number box="[428,477,1180,1204]" pageId="1" pageNumber="32" value="0.38">0.38</number>
times as long as body, lengths of antennal segments 
<number box="[1125,1171,1180,1204]" pageId="1" pageNumber="32" value="2.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="1.0">1–4</number>
